# 6. Fix the incentive problem

## Current weakness

Why would people spend time reviewing or ranking?

## Fix

In the first version, they do it because it is part of their existing work.

Do not depend on public contribution behavior yet.
Depend on internal workflow behavior.

For later networked versions, incentives can become:

* paid review pools
* verified industry reviewers
* portfolio building
* reputation layers
* contest-based creative discovery
* revenue share on adopted branches

But that is not phase one.

Phase one incentive is simple:

> This tool helps the team make better creative decisions faster.

That is enough.

