# What investors would need to see next

To become fundable, you need evidence in four categories.

## 1. Product proof

Show that teams use it on real projects.

Targets:

* 10 to 20 active teams
* 3+ projects per team
* weekly usage from core accounts
* repeated branch comparison behavior

## 2. Workflow ROI

Show measurable benefit.

Examples:

* reduced decision time
* fewer revision cycles
* faster approval rounds
* better audience performance on selected branches
* higher internal alignment

## 3. Retention

Show that once teams use it, they keep using it.

This matters more than signups.

## 4. Clear ICP

Show that one exact customer profile loves it.

For example:

* “mid-sized YouTube story channels publishing weekly”
* “indie film teams in active script development”
* “creative agencies testing narrative campaigns”

