# What not to do

Do not:

* launch with all roles public
* build an open story marketplace first
* lead with philosophy
* depend on consumer virality
* make AI generation the main moat
* keep the product too abstract
* allow uncontrolled infinite branching
* leave IP terms vague
* build five layers before proving one

These would keep the company in “interesting but unfundable” territory.

